      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, blood analog viscosity, temperature) match COU operating envelope within documented tolerances.",
      "rationale": "All five flow-speed test points conducted at 37°C with porcine blood analog. Flow rate controlled to ±0.05 L/min; rotational speed to ±10 RPM. Test conditions replicate nominal COU envelope. Hardware used was new and unaged; no fault states introduced."
